item.title: Strange objects?
item.dc:creator: @Scully Scully
item.description:
@Scully wrote:

Forgot to mention the model thing…lemme go into some detail this time sorry.
Go into class46 and delete everything from [code]// START OF OBJECTS //

// END OF OBJECTS //[/code]

Then go into your models folder and delete the models that the objects are from. This will probably require looking through each zip file so it takes awhile no doubt. If your not worried about your custom items, and NPCs then don’t look for their model id and just delete them from class8 and class5.
